OL,10,FA ceiling collapse inside a student
OL,11,Faccommodation block at Loughborough
OL,12,FUniversity has prompted serious
OL,13,Fconcerns about the condition of
OL,14,Fhousing provided to students across
OL,15,Fthe country.
OL,17,FA video posted to social media earlier
OL,18,Fthis week showed the moment a ceiling
OL,19,Fin a block of flats began leaking as
OL,20,Fthe occupiers in the property watched
OL,21,Fon.
