OL,6,FJust seconds later, the ceiling fell
OL,7,Fthrough completely, leaving what
OL,8,Fappeared to be soil and other debris
OL,9,Fspread across the room and the
OL,10,Fstudent's bed.
OL,12,FThe incident occurred in one of the
OL,13,Fstudent villages located on
OL,14,FLoughborough University campus.
