OL,3,CCeiling collapse at Loughborough
OL,4,Cstudent halls raises safety concerns
OL,6,FWhen ITV News visited the site, the
OL,7,Faffected block had a strong smell of
OL,8,Fdamp and soil and, despite the
OL,9,Fcollapse, only the student who had
OL,10,Foccupied the room where the collapse
OL,11,Fhappened had been moved from the
OL,12,Fbuilding. The person living above had
OL,13,Fnot been moved.
OL,15,FStudents told us it's not the first
OL,16,Ftime a ceiling has collapsed. Earlier
OL,17,Fthis year another ceiling in the same
OL,18,Fblock collapsed leaving similar debris
OL,19,Facross the student's room.
