OL,3,CCeiling collapse at Loughborough
OL,4,Cstudent halls raises safety concerns
OL,6,FAnother student on campus described
OL,7,Fhow they had waited weeks for a basic
OL,8,Ffault in their room to be fixed by the
OL,9,Fmaintenance team.
OL,11,FStudents living in these halls can pay
OL,12,Fup to #10,026.04 per student year for
OL,13,Ftheir accommodation.
OL,15,FSince ITV News reached out to other
OL,16,Fstudents on social media, we've heard
OL,17,Fmultiple similar accounts from
OL,18,Funiversities across the country.
