OL,3,CCeiling collapse at Loughborough
OL,4,Cstudent halls raises safety concerns
OL,6,FSome included no running water from
OL,7,Ftaps for months on end, multiple
OL,8,Fceiling collapses due to damp
OL,9,Fconditions, hot water issues for
OL,10,Fentire academic years and vermin
OL,11,Finfestations that were never solved.
OL,13,FLoughborough University said: "As soon
OL,14,Fas the University was made aware of
OL,15,Fthis issue action was taken to support
OL,16,Fthe student impacted.
OL,18,F"A thorough inspection of the
OL,19,Faccommodation was carried out and the
OL,20,Froot cause of the issue has been
OL,21,Fidentified and repaired.
