OL,6,F"Detailed checks of other rooms in the
OL,7,Fstudent housing block have taken
OL,8,Fplace."
OL,10,FThe collapse is the latest in a series
OL,11,Fof concerns raised about student
OL,12,Fhousing conditions across the UK.
OL,14,FA national survey earlier this year by
OL,15,Fthe National Union of Students UK
OL,16,Ffound that 69% of students had
OL,17,Fexperienced at least one issue with
OL,18,Ftheir accommodation.
